x10.matrix.dist

Class DistMultDupToDist

  • x10.matrix.dist.DistMultDupToDist

  • public class DistMultDupToDist
    Implementation of distributed multiply duplicated matrix and store result in distributed dense block matrix over all places.

    A has 1-D partitioning in nx1 blocks, and B has dense matrix replicated at all n places.
